* **Usage:** You are permitted to download, compile, run, and use this plugin on any Minecraft server, including both commercial (monetized) and non-commercial servers.
* **Private Modification:** You are permitted to make private modifications to the source code solely for use on your own Minecraft server.

### 2. Restrictions
* **No Code Copying / Stealing:** Copying, extracting, adapting, or porting any portion of the source code, logic, algorithms, or ideas of this plugin into other plugins, software, or products is strictly prohibited.
* **No Reselling / Commercial Redistribution:** You may not sell, resell, redistribute, repackage, or publish this software (modified or unmodified) on SpigotMC, BuiltByBit, Modrinth, or any other platform.
* **No Derivative Distribution:** You may not distribute or share modified versions (forks) of this plugin publicly under any circumstances.

